x4freetext: Measurement of the fission cross section of 236-U
relative to 235-U in the range of neutron energies
Correction on layer nonhomogeneity is less than
0.3 percent. Correction on  neutrons scattered on
on neutrons scattered on exp.hall walls 0.30 % .
Correction due to inelastic neutron scattering 7.6 % .
Total error is quadratic sum of all errors
Error of background neutrons scattered on
Error of background neutrons scattered on
Error  due to inelastic neutron scattering
Partial errors are given at EN=3.4 MeV.
Of compiler M.M. Data for Subents 004-012 were not
digitized because data are preliminary. Two pairs of
figures from J,AE and J,YF for the same energy 0.800
MeV and for 0.850 MeV were compared and essential
difference was found between preliminary data of J,AE
Digitized data were added in Subent 013-040 .
